{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a very interesting place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole concept was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The reason for having this at all was that the more intelligent fascists, by the fall of 1944, had seen quite clearly that the war is over and they lost.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They still though, were believing their own propaganda.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this chief of the Sixth District-- the fascist chief of the Sixth District-- really believed that when the Russian armies came under the commandership of Jewish generals, then his life would be spared.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he saved around 500, 600 Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeretzyan-Ara, George.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "George being the first name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeretzyan-Ara was his family name, and he was Armenian in origin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he decided to organize this hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This hospital was staffed by the best Jewish doctors in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who was organized by one of the people who lived in that house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bergessi ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a psychiatrist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was a-- a person who had a very large practice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very interesting man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I would not say that he was a terribly pleasant man and one of my bad experiences are attached to him-- but I-- if we have time I may come back to this later.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll just continue now with the hospital, which was organized and staffed by these Jewish physicians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had approximately 25 different specialties there, and initially they were seeing patients as they came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a-- a [? ambulance ?] service for those who came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course it was free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I managed to see one of the submissions of this Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Yeretzyan-Ara who offered to the Minister of Interior that he will organize a hospital like this in every district in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because as he noted, the Jewish possessions are national treasure.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
